@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener todos los acudientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians

###

### Obtener acudiente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians/1

###

### Crear acudiente
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": 9,
  "doc_type": "CC",
  "doc_number": "1111111111",
  "first_name": "Maria",
  "last_name": "Lopez",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "email": "maria.lopez@test.com",
  "relationship": "Madre",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Actualizar acudiente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Maria Actualizada",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Eliminar acudiente fisicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians/1

###

### Eliminar acudiente logicamente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/guardians/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}
